titleInfo.title: (PC) Watts v. Romero et al
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER signed by Magistrate Judge Carolyn K. Delaney on 4/22/15 ORDERING that the order requiring plaintiff to pay the filing fee for this action (ECF No. 9) is hereby vacated; Plaintiffs request for leave to proceed in forma pauperis (ECF No. 13) is granted; Plaintiff is obligated to pay the statutory filing fee of $350.00 for this action. All fees shall be collected and paid in accordance with this courts order to the Director of the California Department of Corrections and Rehabilitation filed concurrently herewith; The complaint is dismissed with 30 days to amend.(Dillon, M)
